{"tid":1029220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧寵茂：內地醫院非常講效率　港醫護北上建科研基地對兩地有好處","createTime":"2019-02-20T05:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T07:12:15.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"14e31be1fed1186cfd8f153902797799097f5f3f","tid":1029220,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190220/s00001/56e38417a3d76451f068eb43f4306e29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190220%2Fs00001%2F56e38417a3d76451f068eb43f4306e29.jpg&h=ef3dfe3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院日前公布《粵港澳大灣區發展規劃綱要》，當中有關兩地醫療合作的議題引起爭議。港大深圳醫院長盧寵茂接受港台節目訪問時指，內地醫院非常講求效率，呼籲各界多參觀港大深圳醫院，又稱香港醫護人員北上建設科研基地，對兩地都有好處。<br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂表示，港大在大灣區概念開始構思前，已在2011年起於深圳設立醫院，形容是「非常有遠見」，而現時港大僅僅通過數十名香港人手，就建立了擁有600多名醫生及2000多張病牀的港大深圳醫院，規模在香港甚至世界少見。<br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂呼籲各界多上港大深圳醫院參觀，認為可借港大深圳醫院的經驗改善香港醫療服務。他舉例稱，內地醫院現時已推行「智慧醫院」概念，非常講求效率，無論掛號、繳費、看檢查報告全部都是透過手機完成，病人入院至看完症離開醫院，全程只須一個小時。<br />\n<br />\n被問及《綱要》建議會否令本港醫護人才流失，令香港醫護人手更加不足時，他表示是否北上是由醫生自行判斷，強調醫療並非產業，即使本港醫護人員要北上，重點應在教學培訓科研，而非單純診症。他稱若港大或中大醫學院可與內地合作在大灣區建立科研基地，對兩地都有好處。<br />\n<br />\n另外，食衛局昨日表示，政府原則上支持內地指定醫院，以普通載客車輛跨境運送非急重香港病人到香港公院就診，盧寵茂回應有關爭議時，認為上述段落僅是整篇《綱要》中較為不重要的部分，因現時已經「任何人都可以咁做」，呼籲社會不要聚焦有關議題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190220/s00001/1550629016421/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190220%2Fs00001%2F1550629016421%2F&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n80oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=8a4cd1dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190220%2Fs00001%2F1550629016421%2F&h=fd827098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190220/s00001/1550629016421/</a>"},{"pid":"56cbc776dd7532fbd52cacfd0f349c88597d53f0","tid":1029220,"uid":85751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"可以收紅包了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6833d6820ca3c2140da5791d7d28b2e0abc1f056","tid":1029220,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"之前深圳走數清左未？"},{"pid":"fc284d722a460e3a94f71033d4c105865c04477e","tid":1029220,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"大陸洗撚起醫院咩 ,有遠見都講得出<br />\n個撚個大陸閪都黎香港睇"},{"pid":"1af1bf61ce84cbc810716f8e5829f67f51361258","tid":1029220,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"有錢有效率"},{"pid":"30cc18463018dcb3c921d44e134447605596dcc7","tid":1029220,"uid":75384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"先收錢 後睇症 <br />\n跟住做一半手術加你價要即磅水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ab01f1cc2ce0c41f38d8d61aa68369132822ec","tid":1029220,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"他們收紅包的效率就高"},{"pid":"93253546a68ee73a84caa088be156171d5e7957d","tid":1029220,"uid":129739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6833d6820ca3c2140da5791d7d28b2e0abc1f056","tid":1029220,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"之前深圳走數清左未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"差左港大好似十幾億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8f390cea9922d686ac734c9c07dc4b50f189c8","tid":1029220,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"支那茂<br />\n<br />\n上去被內地醫護偷走器官 殺死就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2275d5c401c8cad7b6192a6c084bf9f41a30616","tid":1029220,"uid":4661,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"有效率，乜都吊針先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.epochtimes.com.tw/upload/images/2014/12/30/119117_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F2014%2F12%2F30%2F119117_medium.jpg&h=fdabba8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1863eaed650e721bc62d7e6bd4e5d3173d0a8e29","tid":1029220,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6833d6820ca3c2140da5791d7d28b2e0abc1f056","tid":1029220,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"之前深圳走數清左未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"走數效率高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c674843d811828ab2caa1106c4502b42d2b665","tid":1029220,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2275d5c401c8cad7b6192a6c084bf9f41a30616","tid":1029220,"uid":4661,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"有效率，乜都吊針先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.epochtimes.com.tw/upload/images/2014/12/30/119117_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F2014%2F12%2F30%2F119117_medium.jpg&h=fdabba8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"樣樣野都要比錢先，無錢就next，實快"},{"pid":"5a1fdaed67dd1f96a4d6f971c4ce5395bb69693d","tid":1029220,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"講到咁把炮, 不如問下佢支唔支持中國醫生免試來港執業啦"},{"pid":"1a31698f39c38e990c891e4ea596afa27a30f94f","tid":1029220,"uid":81141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"班港豬醫生係咪都要你上房排檢查 太無效率<br />\n引入強國醫生落黎 個個case吊鹽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c2568e0f759c088e1a7c92c0a292755f478850","tid":1029220,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQpXOL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQpXOL5.jpg&h=9363cbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家講到飛天都冇用<br />\n決定權咪又係我地手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb640cf7f0022a916202c2b1b67cb80bf625f83","tid":1029220,"uid":144024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:12:10.000Z","msg":"其實班官係咪真係離地到咁撚樣呀？<br />\n<br />\n同大灣區合作會可以減輕香港醫療負擔？<br />\n肯定唔撚會。<br />\n<br />\n點解大陸人貴咁多、又要排撚到2046都要黎香港睇醫生？係因為佢地信唔過大陸啲醫院呀。<br />\n<br />\n打疫苗可以無效；一堆蒲田系醫院，睇個感冒吹到大大獲最後要開刀埋單幾萬先落得樓。<br />\n<br />\n我唔排除大陸有名醫（或者好嘅醫生），但係啲人黎係信唔過成個醫療系統同成個體際。<br />\n<br />\n呃開老綜嗰班，排隊睇醫生有乜所謂，反正大把時間。<br />\n香港本土人，點會無啦啦走去大灣區睇？<br />\n有錢黎香港睇嗰班，都有錢啦，何必要拎條命較飛？情願香港睇。"},{"pid":"503c2087cde611c02e02c71e64374a289e10f749","tid":1029220,"uid":236728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:12:10.000Z","msg":"唔work㗎，內地同香港醫療係兩個唔同system, 用詞、流程及處理方式等都唔一樣。<br />\n中醫就可以試吓嘅<br />\n利申：做過中醫藥及醫院嘅IT。"},{"pid":"d92fbf6bf9f9c9a7721bc3b4bed14e487f212dc0","tid":1029220,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d799efaa651577014d4dc8206bdec677ca81dae2","tid":1029220,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"Search&rsquo;港大深圳醫院醫療事故&rsquo;<br />\n好誇張，年年都有人為事故<br />\n<br />\n另外，盧生你咁識扮受傷，證明你都幾臉皮厚，繼續係咁出名既醫院做，唔好返香港"},{"pid":"c6e94ab31b65722527b563ac2551ecd722d94013","tid":1029220,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n死都死快啲"},{"pid":"e9eadf6fcc340146128cf2182bbc48514a1adbfc","tid":1029220,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"好有效率：有錢即醫，冇錢即走。"},{"pid":"999104a4609405f9c196206d78117d2f24023ca8","tid":1029220,"uid":234658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62d9cfc8d10ca245357416a5b243b2f084ab9f47","tid":1029220,"uid":26601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lo2223_7Q2VM_1200x0_ldRcL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flo2223_7Q2VM_1200x0_ldRcL_1200x0.png&h=c22b960c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁下次有事記得上去睇啦，搭車又咁方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee35a610e9d27f19bb5f6f9d278b4e5ea0057fa8","tid":1029220,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"嘩呢個冚家產"}]}